    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1156">
<l>pirivuraikkum vaṉkaṇṇa rāyi ṉaritavar</l>
<l> nalkuva reṉṉu nacai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If he is so cruel as to mention his departure (to me), the hope that he would bestow (his love) must be given up.</l>
            </lg>
